<SYNC Start=840102><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=840306><P Class=ENCC>
-I can't make a decision. Just<br>-Okay. Stay.
<SYNC Start=843935><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=846245><P Class=ENCC>
-Stay.<br>-Stay.
<SYNC Start=847712><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=855688><P Class=ENCC>
Getting so good at that!
<SYNC Start=858088><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=859391><P Class=ENCC>
It was Max's stuff.
<SYNC Start=861484><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=869435><P Class=ENCC>
I love this artichoke thing.
<SYNC Start=872165><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=872371><P Class=ENCC>
Don't tell me what's in it.<br>The diet starts tomorrow.
<SYNC Start=875829><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=880379><P Class=ENCC>
You remember Janice.
<SYNC Start=882677><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=883749><P Class=ENCC>
Vividly.
<SYNC Start=885444><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=885951><P Class=ENCC>
-How are you?<br>-I am fantastic.
<SYNC Start=889682><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=889889><P Class=ENCC>
Now.
<SYNC Start=890947><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=892558><P Class=ENCC>
