<SYNC Start=899328><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=900633><P Class=ENCC>
It's like we were never apart.
<SYNC Start=902658><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=903002><P Class=ENCC>
