<SYNC Start=919852><P Class=ENCC>
-Hi.<br>-Hi, l' m Sandy.
<SYNC Start=921285><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=921487><P Class=ENCC>
Sandy, hi. Come on in.
