This is how you greet guests?
<SYNC Start=947168><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=947379><P Class=ENCC>
If I showed up with my new girlfriend,<br>she wouldn't be welcome?
<SYNC Start=952043><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=952584><P Class=ENCC>
