<SYNC Start=998663><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=999131><P Class=ENCC>
And then your face exploded?
<SYNC Start=1001395><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1002835><P Class=ENCC>
No.
<SYNC Start=1004063><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1004703><P Class=ENCC>
Okay. I was at the airport<br>getting into a cab...
<SYNC Start=1008503><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1008741><P Class=ENCC>
