<SYNC Start=1018145><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1018350><P Class=ENCC>
The next thing, she just<br>starts pulling me out by my hair!
<SYNC Start=1022446><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
