...and three more cabs show up.
<SYNC Start=1028318><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1028527><P Class=ENCC>
So as I'm going to get into a cab,<br>she tackles me!
<SYNC Start=1033157><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1033599><P Class=ENCC>
And I hit my head on the curb<br>and cut my lip on my whistle.
<SYNC Start=1038764><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1042541><P Class=ENCC>
Everybody having fun at the party?
<SYNC Start=1044873><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
