<SYNC Start=1245675><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1246044><P Class=ENCC>
You listen to me!<br>You listen to me!
<SYNC Start=1248274><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1248513><P Class=ENCC>
One of these times, it's just gonna be<br>your last chance with me!
