Somebody kiss me! It's midnight!<br>Somebody kiss me!
<SYNC Start=1465360><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1465597><P Class=ENCC>
All right! All right!
<SYNC Start=1467497><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1468099><P Class=ENCC>
There!
<SYNC Start=1469498><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1475941><P Class=ENCC>
I wanted this to work so much.
<SYNC Start=1478501><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1479177><P Class=ENCC>
I'm still in there.
<SYNC Start=1480906><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1481146><P Class=ENCC>
Changing his diapers.<br>Picking his fleas.
<SYNC Start=1484172><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1484783><P Class=ENCC>
But he's just phoning it in.
<SYNC Start=1487183><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1488954><P Class=ENCC>
It's hard that something you love<br>so much doesn't love you back.
<SYNC Start=1494153><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1494359><P Class=ENCC>
I think that bitch cracked my tooth.
<SYNC Start=1497453><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
